---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Contact | newtricks.ai" description="Contact newtricks.ai">
  <section class="mx-auto w-full max-w-3xl px-6 py-16">
    <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-muted">Contact</p>
    <h1 class="mt-3 font-display text-6xl uppercase leading-none text-zinc-100">Let’s connect</h1>
    <div class="mt-8 space-y-5 text-zinc-300">
      <p>For now, the best way to reach out is through social channels while the full contact workflow is in progress.</p>
      <ul class="space-y-2">
        <li><a class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-phosphor hover:text-signal" href="https://x.com/newtricksai">X / Twitter → @newtricksai</a></li>
        <li><a class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-phosphor hover:text-signal" href="https://github.com/chrisyerga">GitHub → @chrisyerga</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
